<p>
A "place holder" variable in the method signature located between the parentheses.

For example, the integer variable <tt>number</tt> is the parameter:
	<pre>public void exampleMethod(int number)</pre>

<br />
When the method is called, the variable is assigned a value supplied
as an <a href="glossary.php?term=argument">argument</a> in the call.
</p>
